description:
What is the work of the Holy Spirit? What parallels exist between the work of Nehemiah during the time of the rebuilding of Jerusalem and the work of the Holy Spirit in last day events? 

In this typological Bible study on the book of Nehemiah, Walter Veith applies lessons to Gods remnant church.  Nehemiah serves as a type of the function of the Holy Spirit. Without a right understanding of the function of the Holy Spirit, Gods people can be led into a dangerous Pentecostal euphoria. Learn about the true function of the Holy Spiritdeep soul searching and separation from all that wars against the law of God. 

Discover the essence of the revival of true godliness thats needed among us today.
